DEVICE DATA INGESTION PROCESS FLOW
This process flow combines various Nifi processors to pipeline, prepare, transform and ingest Device data into Elasticsearch for visualization by Kibana.
Split Device Array Object Process Group
Retrieve all split properties as Flow-Attributes

Routeing on content (if data is present or null).
Present - route data for renaming
null - terminate routing

This process flow splits all device properties which are array objects into individual flow files using a SplitJson processor and then passes the resut into a JSONTransform Processor which renames the inner properties by appending the parent name.
Add general device data and all split property attributes into individual flowfiles
